@startuml Fase2_VistaProcessos

title Fase 2 - Vista de Processos (Sequencia Principal)

skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Profissional de Saude" as User
participant "Web SPA" as SPA
participant "Simulacoes API" as API
participant "SimulacaoService" as SERVICE
participant "LLM Adapter" as LLM

== 1. Iniciar Sessao ==
User -> SPA : seleciona caso e inicia simulacao
SPA -> API : POST /api/simulacoes/sessoes
API -> SERVICE : IniciarSessaoAsync(casoId)
SERVICE --> API : sessao criada
API --> SPA : 201 Created + sessao

== 2. Conversa Clinica ==
loop Enquanto sessao ativa
  User -> SPA : envia pergunta ao paciente virtual
  SPA -> API : POST /api/simulacoes/sessoes/{sessaoId}/mensagens
  API -> SERVICE : ProcessarNovaMensagemAsync()
  SERVICE -> LLM : gerar resposta contextualizada
  LLM --> SERVICE : resposta do paciente virtual
  SERVICE --> API : interacoes atualizadas
  API --> SPA : 200 OK + resposta da IA
end

== 3. Consulta de Estado ==
SPA -> API : GET /api/simulacoes/sessoes/{sessaoId}
API -> SERVICE : ObterSessaoPorIdAsync()
SERVICE --> API : estado da sessao
API --> SPA : 200 OK + historico

== 4. Conclusao e Avaliacao ==
User -> SPA : conclui simulacao
SPA -> API : POST /api/simulacoes/sessoes/{sessaoId}/concluir
API -> SERVICE : ConcluirSessaoAsync()
SERVICE --> API : sessao finalizada + avaliacao
API --> SPA : 200 OK
SPA --> User : apresenta feedback final

@enduml
